name: THE EMPRESS III ~ Timeless Tarot
description: You are full of love and feeling very comfortable in your own skin. You may be feeling like you have just found your niche. At the moment, you have everything you need to be productive. Get creative or spend some time in the garden connecting with nature and manifesting your next steps. Your soul tribe supports you fully and you are a very nurturing leader. (Upright:Abundance,fertility,family,security,growth;Reversed:Confusion,stagnation,domestic issues,co-dependency)
